    {
      "title": "Set up",
      "content": "Two pieces sum to 108: x + y = 108. The longer piece is 8 more than 4 times the shorter: x = 4y + 8."
    },
    {
      "title": "Solve",
      "content": "Substitute: (4y + 8) + y = 108 $\\Rightarrow$ 5y = 100 $\\Rightarrow$ y = 20. Then x = 4(20) + 8 = 88."
    },
    {
      "title": "Answer",
      "content": "x = 88, which confirms <strong>D</strong> &mdash; <strong>D</strong> is correct."
    }
